    "Now <span class=\"person\">Korah</span>, the son of <span class=\"person\">Izhar</span>, the son of <span class=\"person\">Kohath</span>, the son of <span class=\"person\">Levi</span>, and Dathan and Abiram, the sons of Eliab, and <span class=\"place\">On</span>, the son of Peleth, sons of <span class=\"person\">Reuben</span>, took men:",
