    "And from Mattanah to Nahaliel: and from Nahaliel to Bamoth:",
    "And from Bamoth in the valley, that is in the country of <span class=\"person\">Moab</span>, to the top of Pisgah, which looketh toward Jeshimon.",
    "And <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> sent messengers unto Sihon king of the Amorites, saying,",
