    "And the children of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> set forward, and pitched in the plains of <span class=\"person\">Moab</span> on this side <span class=\"place\">Jordan</span> by <span class=\"place\">Jericho</span>.",
    "And Balak the son of Zippor saw all that <span class=\"place\">Israel</span> had done to the Amorites.",
