    "He sent messengers therefore unto Balaam the son of <span class=\"person\">Beor</span> to Pethor, which is by the river of the land of the children of his people, to call him, saying, Behold, there is a people come out from <span class=\"place\">Egypt</span>: behold, they cover the face of the earth, and they abide over against me:",
