    "And the border shall go down to <span class=\"place\">Jordan</span>, and the goings out of it shall be at the salt sea: this shall be your land with the coasts thereof round about.",
    "And <span class=\"person\">Moses</span> commanded the children of <span class=\"place\">Israel</span>, saying, This is the land which ye shall inherit by lot, which the LORD commanded to give unto the nine tribes, and to the half tribe:",
    "For the tribe of the children of <span class=\"person\">Reuben</span> according to the house of their fathers, and the tribe of the children of <span class=\"person\">Gad</span> according to the house of their fathers, have received their inheritance; and half the tribe of <span class=\"person\">Manasseh</span> have received their inheritance:",
